{"data":[{"id":561510903,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ffb84d62bb13bdec7f866e86a1b2664c","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":12,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561510903","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545974064,"updated_time":1545974064,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我最想说的是，知乎不是发表论文的地方，知乎就一论坛社区，和天涯猫扑贴吧好不到哪儿去，在知乎发表论文，未免让人笑掉大牙。在知乎发表只有博眼球，涨粉骗赞甚至营销接广告的嫌疑，真有本事，发表学术论文！参加学术会议！其他的，都是可耻的行径。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e关于数学论文的发表，既然你都说了是这样重量级的成果，那么数学四大期刊请随便挑一个发表。当然最推荐的还是最有影响力的ANNALS OF MATHEMATICS：\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//annals.math.princeton.edu/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003eannals.math.princeton.edu\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e/\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e20年来国内能在ANNALS OF MATHEMATICS上发表的论文不过20来篇，著名数学家陈省身、华罗庚等都在ANNALS OF MATHEMATICS上发表过论文。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果数学四大期刊有一个录用，再到知乎来谈证明了的事情，不然只能说是造谣生事，沽名钓誉，不可理喻了。\u003c/p\u00